{
  "stem": "24130.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister was-- Lilly-- was in the back of him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she saw this German want to hit him with a club.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she stretched out her hand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he hit her across the hand, Lilly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She came up on the-- on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had-- [SOB] her hand was swollen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father says, I saw you threw away the basket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I says, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I says, what was in that basket?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he says, that was my talis and tefillin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His prayer shawl that he had it since-- [SOB] since he got married that my mother bought it for him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SOBBING] So I says, daddy, why didn't you tell me that what I have in that basket?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would have give my life to save it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SOBBING] But I just till this day, I feel so bad that I threw away his prayer shawl and his tefillin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CRYING] So Lilly had a swollen hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came up on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had there-- 10-- 10 breads and a pail.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't know it was an empty pail.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What in that pail?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What that pail is for?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we said to my father, we took the breads to share for everybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were pushing people in, how much they could just push in people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it got so crowded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we took the 10 breads, and we-- to share the breads.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to my father, how come there's no water?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a pail.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why isn't there any water in that pail?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because bread and water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father knew right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, we don't have a bathroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, this is for the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, this is for the bathroom?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
